description:
Iznajmljuje se prekrasan četverosoban stan površine 91 m2 na četvrtom katu novije stambene zgrade u Trnju - Trnjanska cesta.  
    
 Stan se sastoji od:  
 - ulaznog hodnika;  
 - dnevnog boravka s prostorom za blagovanje i kuhinjom;  
 - ostave;  
 - tri spavaće sobe;  
 - kupaone s toaletom;  
 - dodatnog toaleta;  
 - balkona i zatvorene loggie.  
    
 Izvrsna lokacija; blizina tramvaja i busa; blizina svih potrebnih sadržaja.  
 Režije po stvarnoj potrošnji (plinsko etažno grijanje).  
    
 Polog u visini jedne mjesečne najamnine  
       
 _______________________________________________________________  
 ENGLISH:  
 A beautiful three bedroom apartment of 91 m2 on the fourth floor of a newer residential building in Trnje - Trnjanska cesta.     

The apartment consists of:  
- entrance hall;  
- living room with dining area and kitchen;  
- pantry;  
- three bedrooms;  
- bathroom with toilet;  
- additional toilet;  
- balcony and closed loggia.    

Great location; proximity to trams and buses; close to all necessary facilities.  
Charges by actual consumption (central gas heating ).     
Deposit in the amount of one month's rent.     

